Package temp.fibHeap.stixar.graph Description

Core package for graph classes and interfaces.

This package provides classes and interfaces for graphs. Implementations of directed and undirected graphs together with a rich attribute mechanism, are provided. Interfaces include the stixar.graph.Node and stixar.graph.Edge interfaces, allowing users to implement graphs with relative ease by extending their own application specific classes.

Subpackages include
  • Graph generators.
  • Search
  • Paths and shortest paths.
  • Connectivity algorithms.
  • Editing algorithms.
  • Property checkers.
  • Flow analysis.
